p 6: Set the Coupon Code Actions</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In the &#8220;Actions&#8221; section, select the discount type for your coupon code. You can choose from percent off, fixed amount, or free shipping. Then, enter the discount amount or percentage.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained  inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\"><div style=\"max-width:752px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20height=&#x27;475&#x27;%20width=&#x27;752&#x27;%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%\"></div><img data-gatsby-image-ssr=\"\" data-wp-inline-image=\"2\" data-main-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;transform:translateZ(0);transition:opacity 250ms linear;width:100%;will-change:opacity;opacity:0\" sizes=\"(min-width: 752px) 752px, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/_gatsby/image/f5466d2e038605eb62c433a2d6c239ea/48fcf1d4effcf510caa0d1fe88e9ccb6/how-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2-4.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2-4.png&amp;a=w%3D188%26h%3D119%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2023-03-13T07%3A52%3A55\" data-srcset=\"/_gatsby/image/f5466d2e038605eb62c433a2d6c239ea/48fcf1d4effcf510caa0d1fe88e9ccb6/how-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2-4.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2-4.png&amp;a=w%3D188%26h%3D119%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2023-03-13T07%3A52%3A55 188w,/_gatsby/image/f5466d2e