by/image/f5466d2e038605eb62c433a2d6c239ea/43eedc786522e0590599741c0af21081/how-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2-4.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2Fhow-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2-4.png&a=w%3D752%26h%3D475%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&cd=2023-03-13T07%3A52%3A55 752w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 752px) 752px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":752,\"height\":475},\"alt\":\"\",\"className\":\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"2\"}</script></figure></div>\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 7: Save the Cart Price Rule</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Click on the &#8220;Save and Continue Edit&#8221; button at the top right corner of the page to save your coupon code.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://webguru.dev/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/how-to-create-coupon-codes-in-magento-2-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"-5\" height=\"-1\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Step 8: Test the Coupon Code</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>To test your coupon code, add a product to your cart and enter the coupon code at checkout. The discount should be applied to your order total.</p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained  inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\"><div style=\"max-width:695px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20height=&#x27;332&#x27;%20width=&#x27;695&#x27;%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100